description:
Check out the amazing apartment we stayed in: https://bit.ly/3ErDOf0
Welcome back to Japan everybody where we are heading out to find Tokyo's most EXCLUSIVE cafe's and restaurants...and by exclusive I mean I had to pay someone in Taiwan to get me reservations here...that's how hard it is to get them.

  Grab our Tokyo Map https://bit.ly/417zquC 
 Plus buy 2 get 1 free on maps for the next 48 hours   https://flyingthenestshop.com/collections/map-guides
Use the discount code: MAPSALE

For those people interested in how much we spent to book the Kirby cafe... click here https://flyingthenest.kit.com/48620a49f1 

Let's find out if the 
- Harry Potter Cafe in Tokyo
- Pokemon Pikachu Cafe in Tokyo
- Kirby Cafe in Tokyo
and a bonus one....worth the hoops you have to jump through?

Thanks to the amazing team who partnered up with us to show you their incredible apartment in Shibuya: https://bit.ly/3ErDOf0

Book the Harry Potter Cafe here (official website): https://bit.ly/4hwdfEc

Hi, we are Stephen, Jess, Hunter and baby Koa - an Australian family who have had quite the journey. After travelling the world as a couple in 2020 we had our very first baby, we then spent the following year self-converted a van before moving into it full-time to drive around Australia. Cut to 2023 we welcomed our second child Koa into the world before resuming full-time travel around the world.
